004import java.time.LocalDate;

006
007public class DateCollectionPredicateBuilder<T> extends ComparableCollectionPredicateBuilder<T, LocalDate>
008        implements ContainsPredicateBuilder<T, LocalDate>, EmptyPredicateBuilder<T> {
009    public DateCollectionPredicateBuilder(final BinaryQueryPredicate predicate,
010            final Function<QueryPredicate, CombinationQueryPredicate<T>> combinationFn) {
011        super(predicate, combinationFn, PredicateFormatter::format);
012    }
